{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act18side", "eventName": "塵影餘音", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "LE-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "春之祭", "storyInfo": "在沉靜的大提琴聲中，黑鍵回想起一些塵封已久的往事。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltstrongpoint", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和陛下有血脈聯繫的人......就只剩這些了？", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那兩個女人下手太快太狠，這已經是極限了。", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是覺得，陛下留下的旋律不應該這麼隨隨便便地——", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你想怎麼辦？", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得我們還是應該穩重一點......", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穩重？我們的人每天都在被殺，你還敢說穩重？這是最後的機會了！", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下的血脈與陛下的旋律結合，就算不能復現陛下全部的力量，至少......", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......到底幾歲？兩歲？三歲？"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我正站在一片破敗的建築中間，茫然地環顧四周。"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶我來的人告訴我，我的父親和母親已經死於私刑，而那時的我還無法理解什麼是私刑，什麼是死。"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他還說，從今以後，這裡就是我的家，我將成為偉大計畫的一部分，運氣好的話，我會成為萊塔尼亞的下一任統治者。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不懂。完全聽不懂。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能懵懵懂懂地意識到，我的那個房間，每天上午會有陽光直射進來的房間，似乎回不去了。"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經說過了，把人當成塵世之音的容器，這種事情不可能成功的......", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你早知道不可能？計畫實行之前你明確表示反對了嗎？現在倒好，人死了，你倒跳出來說風涼話了？晚了！", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是，我......", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我告訴你，這不是浪費，這是為了成功必須付出的代價。", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要他們之中能有一個活下來，我們就沒必要像做賊一樣躲在這種窮鄉僻壤了！", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞、烏薩斯、卡西米爾......對我們的計畫感興趣的人有的是！只要能成功，我們就能借來他們的軍隊，向那兩個女人復仇！", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天，到這之後一直照顧著我們的大姐姐不見了。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大姐姐不見後，那些會給我們送飯，但和我們不住在一起的人吵了起來。"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是聽不懂他們在吵什麼，只知道，那個會給我們哼歌的大姐姐，好像不會回來了。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那首歌好像是這麼唱的："}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天空湛藍晴朗，"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "微風輕聲歌唱；"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "河水潺潺流淌，"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的心充滿希望。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌曲似乎還有後半段，但大姐姐從來沒有唱過。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次怎麼樣，我問你，這次怎麼樣？", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可人還是死了......", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死了又怎麼樣？我們已經在進步了！", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下次我們把手術室搬到更遠的地方，用阻隔聲音的材料裝修一下......會成功的！", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天氣冷了又暖。"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一開始的時候，每當有人消失，那些人就會大吵特吵。"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來，他們漸漸不吵了，但我們的餐食越來越差，好在吃飯的人也越來越少，所以還能填飽肚子。"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概人就是這樣的東西，一不小心就消失不見了。"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的東西也一樣。"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "某個老奶奶的拐杖，某個大哥哥的音樂盒，某個叔叔愛不釋手的法杖和源石骰子......"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但有些東西會留下來，比如那位大姐姐愛唱的歌。"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有個孩子學會了那首歌，他常把那首歌掛在嘴邊。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們——我們究竟在做什麼？！", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下的血脈被我們保護下來，最後卻......死在我們手上......", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清醒一點，這是必要的代價！為了讓陛下的血脈掌握相應的力量，這是必須付出的犧牲！", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們對塵世之音的瞭解已經越來越多了，很快就能成功的！", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可那些死去的人......", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我們別再搞這種瘋狂的實驗了......我們隱姓埋名，教育剩下的這幾個，沒准他們也能像陛下一樣......", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別做夢了，塵世之音是必需的！", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來，又過了一年，或者兩年，我不知道。"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只剩下我和那個孩子。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每當那些人到房間裡來的時候，我都嚇得全身發抖。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這時，那個孩子就會安慰我，告訴我沒事，然後主動站到那些人面前。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等他們走後，他就會給我唱起那首歌。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我的心充滿希望。”"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們在這待了這麼久，就算是孩子，也該知道是怎麼回事了。", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們畢竟是陛下僅存的血脈，我也不想搞得太難看。下一個輪到誰，你們倆自己決定吧。", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次我們的技術有了很大的改進......也許會成功......也說不定。所以，沒准這次接受實驗的那個人，會......成為很厲害很厲害的術師哦。", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們兩個誰都不傻。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個貴族裝束的人前幾次也這麼說，可離開房間的那些人誰也沒回來。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我雙腿發抖，偷偷看了看旁邊的孩子，他的嘴唇也變得煞白。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想消失，我也不想讓他消失，但是......"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他注意到我的眼神，扭過頭來，顫抖著對我抬起嘴角。"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我來吧。”"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽見他開口，我再也支撐不住，兩腿一軟，跪倒在地。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一個人在空蕩蕩的房間裡住了兩個月。"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，一個下雨的晚上，那個孩子被抬了過來，雙目緊閉，咬著嘴唇，但他活著。"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為奇跡真的發生了，可幾天之後，他又從房間裡被抬走，從此像其他人一樣消失不見。"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "臨走之前，他還在哼那首歌。"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我的心充滿希望。”"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltstrongpoint", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又過了幾天，終於輪到我了。"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一路跟著那兩個人走，一路看到好多以前從未見到過的房間，裡面是各種各樣的裝置和儀器。"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們走到一間小小的房間裡，裡面的一切都是白的。"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個穿高塔術師衣服的人讓我躺在床上。她戴上了白色的口罩和手套，看起來很怪異。"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她把一個面罩扣在我的臉上，然後我就什麼都不知道了。"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是在那些人的歡呼聲中醒來的。"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛一醒來，立刻就覺得自己的腦袋裡面有岩漿正在沸騰，幾乎要把我的眼睛烤熟。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇痛持續了......多長時間？幾天？幾個星期？幾個月？"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltstrongpoint", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，隨著時間流逝，疼痛漸漸減弱，最後變成了偶爾會劇烈發作，但很快就能恢復的頭痛。"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我等著他們像對別人一樣把我抬出去，但他們沒有。"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們反而開始對我獻殷勤，給我加餐，放我在庭院裡亂跑。"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們還給我上課，教我讀，教我寫，還有，教我源石技藝。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們把屬於那個叔叔的法杖和源石骰子珍而重之地交給了我，說它們曾經是陛下的收藏，讓我一定要好好珍惜。"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從那以後，我每展示出一點法術上的天賦，都能換來一片肉麻的讚美聲。"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，這樣的日子也沒持續多久。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個孩子......是不是到此為止了？", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在看來，就算我們把他逼到極限，他最多也就只能和落單的女皇之聲扳扳手腕......", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不，像之前那個孩子一樣，我們把“塵世之音”的能量流動調整一下......", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了吧。", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怕什麼，這次我們再改進——", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行！！", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你敢跟我頂嘴？！", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼多段“塵世之音”，現在已經只有這一段還能被奏響了；十五個和陛下有血緣聯繫的人，現在也只剩下這一個了！", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把他培養起來，我們或許還能流亡到其他國家去換個一官半職，最重要的是，陛下的血脈還能流傳下去。", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把他也像那個孩子一樣毀了，我們就只能集體自裁以謝陛下了！！", "name": "畏首畏尾的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "肆無忌憚的術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodcracle", "channel": "burn", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第二天，他們也不見了。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是什麼自裁，而是他們總掛在嘴邊的女皇之聲來了。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我坐在空蕩蕩的房間裡，聽著外面的喊殺聲，心裡反而有些快意。"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些人不是最喜歡說什麼“陛下的血脈”了嗎？"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們最害怕的事就要發生了，受詛咒的血脈就要斷絕了。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbreak", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個穿著華麗的人破門而入。"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是女皇之聲吧。"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女皇之聲看著我，既沒有放下武器，也沒有發動攻擊，大概是在猶豫。"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還猶豫什麼呢？"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我抓起法杖對準女皇之聲，源石骰子在我身邊環繞起來。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他果然以我完全無法想像的速度衝了過來，手裡的銅管樂器狠狠敲在我頭上。"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hammer", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodcracle", "channel": "burn", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以那一擊為分界，我短暫的人生被分為兩截。"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏提卡伯爵忘記了自己是如何坐上這把帶手銬的椅子，只有不時發作的頭痛提醒他，他腦子裡還有巫王在塵世留下的最後的旋律。"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的伯爵代理人帶著嫌惡告訴他，那是“不可說的人”的遺物，已經和他的身體不可分割。"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他完全不知道，自己是怎麼和那東西融為一體的。"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他現在想起來了。"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他該怎麼辦？"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能怎麼辦？"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}